com.google.api.client.googleapis
Class MethodOverrideIntercepter

java.lang.Object
  com.google.api.client.googleapis.MethodOverrideIntercepter
All Implemented Interfaces:
HttpExecuteIntercepter
public class MethodOverrideIntercepter
extends Object
implements HttpExecuteIntercepter

HTTP request execute intercepter for Google API's that wraps HTTP requests -- other than GET or POST -- inside of a POST request and uses "X-HTTP-Method-Override" header to specify the actual HTTP method.

It is useful when a firewall only allows the GET and POST methods, or if the underlying HTTP library (LowLevelHttpTransport) does not support the HTTP method.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Yaniv Inbar
